The paper is about Visual Question Answering (VQA), which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also introduces a new dataset and model for deeper reasoning, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper evaluates several baseline models and describes a novel model, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
